      <h2>Tools & Features Used</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Part Studios:</strong> Simultaneous part design across users</li>
        <li><strong>Assembly Studio:</strong> Linked parts into movable mechanical groups</li>
        <li><strong>In-context Editing:</strong> Sketched features based on existing assemblies</li>
        <li><strong>Variables Studio:</strong> Controlled shared parameters for scaling and references</li>
        <li><strong>Branching:</strong> Created parallel ideas and merged clean versions</li>
        <li><strong>Comment Threads:</strong> Left feedback and marked requested changes</li>
      </ul>

